nce-2000-number-one-dark-souls|website=USgamer|publisher=Gamer Network|accessdate=2015-08-11|date=2015-08-11|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150811193155/http://www.usgamer.net/articles/the-15-best-games-since-2000-number-one-dark-souls|archivedate=2015-08-11|deadurl=yes}}</ref>该游戏的PC版亦被[[Rock,_Paper,_Shotgun|Rock, Paper, Shotgun]]评为“PC上最佳RPG游戏”。<ref name="rockpapershotgun">{{cite web|title=The 50 Best RPG On PC|url=https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2015/07/10/best-rpg/8/|website=Rock, Paper, Shotgun|accessdate=2016-02-29|date=2015-07-10|deadurl=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160323012157/https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2015/07/10/best-rpg/8/|archive-date=2016-03-23}}</ref>2016年，黑暗靈魂在[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]]所列出的“迄今为止最佳角色扮演游戏列表（Best RPGs of all time list）”中排行第五。<ref>{{Cite web|title = The best RPGs of all time|url = http://www.pcgamer.com/the-best-rpgs-of-all-time-1/|website = PC Gamer|access-date = 2016-02-19|archive-date = 2016-11-27|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161127163957/http://www.pcgamer.com/the-best-rpgs-of-all-time-1/|dead-url = no}}</ref>

== 影响 ==
黑暗靈魂被认为是[[第七世代游戏机历史|第七世代游戏机]]中最杰出的电子游戏之一，<ref name="Kill Screen influence">{{cite web|url=http://killscreendaily.com/articles/articles/feature/how-do-you-make-rpg-after-dark-souls/|title=How Do You Make An RPG After Dark Souls?|publisher=''[[Kill_Screen|Kill Screen]]''|last=Breault|first=Chris|date=2014-02-24|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150828193953/http://killscreendaily.com/articles/articles/feature/how-do-you-make-rpg-after-dark-souls/|archivedate=2015-08-28|accessdate=2017-02-16}}</ref>由于黑暗之魂的成功，诸多游戏都受魂系列的影响，如《[[天命_(遊戲)|天命]]》、<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/130638-Destiny-Inspired-by-Dark-Souls-Monster-Hunter-Bungie-Says|title=Destiny Inspired by Dark Souls, Monster Hunter, Bungie Says|publisher=''[[The_Escapist_(magazine)|The Escapist]]''|last=Slabaugh|first=Brett|date=2013-12-18|accessdate=2017-02-16|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304222226/http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/130638-Destiny-Inspired-by-Dark-Souls-Monster-Hunter-Bungie-Says|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[异种国度|异化]]》、<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.polygon.com/2014/8/22/6056895/alienation-dark-demon-souls-ps4|title=How Dark Souls influenced Alienation, the next game from Resogun's developer|publisher=''[[Polygon.com|Polygon.com]]''|last=Tach|first=Dave|date=2014-08-22|accessdate=2017-02-16|archive-date=2016-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160424182028/http://www.polygon.com/2014/8/22/6056895/alienation-dark-demon-souls-ps4|dead-url=no}}</ref>《{{link-en|堕落之王|Lords of the Fallen}}》、<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/lords-of-the-fallen-dev-talks-dark-souls-compariso/1100-6424474/|title=Lords of the Fallen Dev Talks Dark Souls Comparisons|publisher=''[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]''|last=Makuch|first=Eddie|date=2015-01-05|accessdate=2017-02-16|archive-date=2015-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150407062821/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/lords-of-the-fallen-dev-talks-dark-souls-compariso/1100-6424474/|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[鹽與聖所|盐与避难所]]》、<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.polygon.com/2014/8/28/6080383/salt-and-sanctuary-video-preview-ps4-ps-vita|title=How Salt and Sanctuary reimagines Dark Souls as a 2D action-platformer|publisher=[[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]]|last=McElroy|first=Griffin|date=2013-08-28|accessdate=2017-02-16|archive-date=2016-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160316221758/http://www.polygon.com/2014/8/28/6080383/salt-and-sanctuary-video-preview-ps4-ps-vita|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[鏟子騎士|铲子骑士]]》、<ref name="Kill Screen influence" /><ref>{{citation |url=http://www.usgamer.net/articles/game-dev-recipes-shovel-knight |title=Game Dev Recipes: Shovel Knight |author=Williams, Mike |date=2014-05-24 |accessdate=2014-05-26 |publisher=[[Eurogamer|USgamer]] |archive-date=2014-05-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140525144706/http://www.usgamer.net/articles/game-dev-recipes-shovel-knight |dead-url=no }}</ref>《{{link-en|泰坦之魂|Titan Souls}}》、<ref name="Kill Screen influence" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pcgamer.com/titan-souls-2/|title=Titan Souls|publisher=''[[PCGamer|PCGamer]]''|last=Hamilton|first=Andi|date=2015-04-13|accessdate=2017-02-16|archive-date=2016-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309155711/http://www.pcgamer.com/titan-souls-2/|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[挺進地牢|挺進地牢]]》、<ref>{{cite web|last1=Crooks|first1=Dave|title=How to Get Started in Enter the Gungeon on PS4|url=http://blog.us.playstation.com/2016/04/05/how-to-get-started-in-enter-the-gungeon-on-ps4/|website=PlayStation.Blog|accessdate=2016-04-18|archive-date=2017-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170731002957/https://blog.us.playstation.com/2016/04/05/how-to-get-started-in-enter-the-gungeon-on-ps4/|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[巫师3：狂猎|巫师3：狂猎]]》、<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-11-19-the-witcher-3-what-is-a-next-gen-rpg | title=The Witcher 3: What is a next-gen RPG? | work=Eurogamer.net | date=2013-11-28 | accessdate=2016-09-10 | last=Purchese | first=Robert | archive-date=2017-06-11 | archive-url=https://archive.is/20170611124734/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-11-19-the-witcher-3-what-is-a-next-gen-rpg | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.express.co.uk/entertainment/gaming/567240/Witcher-3-Dark-Souls-big-influence-CD-Projekt-RED-Wild-Hunt | title=Witcher 3: Why Dark Souls has proved a big influence, new details on 200+ hours gameplay | work=Daily Express | date=2015-03-30 | accessdate=2016-09-10 | last=Jones | first=Gary | archive-date=2017-06-11 | archive-url=https://archive.is/20170611124916/http://www.express.co.uk/entertainment/gaming/567240/Witcher-3-Dark-Souls-big-influence-CD-Projekt-RED-Wild-Hunt | dead-url=no }}</ref>《[[仁王_(游戏)|仁王]]》等。

汲取了《黑暗之魂》及From Software前序作品《恶魔之魂》特色的这一类游戏，被称作“魂类”或“类黑魂”游戏（{{lang-en|Souls-Like}}）；特别地，由From Software开发的几款作品，合称为[[魂系列|魂系列]]（{{lang-en|Souls Series}}）。这一系列名称原由玩家群体讨论使用，但随后也被研究与开发人员丰富其定义，如关卡设计与游玩体验等<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.diva-portal.org/smash/get/diva2:935733/FULLTEXT01.pdf|title=Examining the Souls's Series Level Design|author=Valdemar Ribbing , Laban Melander|format=pdf|date=2016-05|language=en|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200704100433/http://www.diva-portal.org/smash/get/diva2:935733/FULLTEXT01.pdf|archivedate=2020-07-04|access-date=2020-07-04|dead-url=no}}中文翻译可参考{{cite web|url=https://www.gcores.com/articles/93781|title=译介 - 用科学的方式研究“魂”系列游戏的关卡设计(上)|website=[[机核|机核]]|accessdate=2020-07-04|archive-date=2020-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200705071616/https://www.gcores.com/articles/93781|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一些游戏平台，也开始以“魂系列类型”称呼这一类游戏<ref>{{cite web|url=https://store.steampowered.com/tags/zh-tw/Souls-like/?l=schinese|title=魂系列类型游戏|website=[[Steam|Steam]]|accessdate=2020-07-04|archive-date=2020-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200704103608/https://store.steampowered.com/tags/zh-tw/Souls-like/?l=schinese|dead-url=no}}</ref>；这同时也伴随了「“魂系列”是不是一种新的[[游戏类型|游戏类型]]（{{lang-en|Game genre}}）」的讨论<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.reddit.com/r/videogamescience/comments/6muf9j/do_we_need_a_soulslike_genre_game_makers_toolkit/|title=Do We Need a Soulslike Genre?|author=Mark Brown|language=en}}</ref>。

== 续作 ==

游戏的续作《[[黑暗靈魂II|黑暗靈魂II]]》于2012年12月7日的[[斯派克電子遊戲大獎|Spike电子游戏大赏]]公开，预计登录的平台有[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]、[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]和[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.shacknews.com/article/76973/dark-souls-2-announced |title=Dark Souls 2 announced – Video Game News, Videos and File Downloads for PC and Console Games at |publisher=Shacknews.com |date= |accessdate=2012-12-08 |archive-date=2012-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121209203651/http://www.shacknews.com/article/76973/dark-souls-2-announced |dead-url=no }}</ref>传闻新游戏制作人向《[[Edge_(杂志)|Edge]]》透露，魂系列的难度可能会降低。[[万代南梦宫|万代南梦宫]]的发言人Brian Hong在[[电子娱乐展|电子娱乐展]]向粉丝们保证，《黑暗靈魂II》将是“格外地难（viciously hard）”。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://venturebeat.com/2013/06/11/e2-2013-dark-souls-2/ |title=Namco Bandai assures fans that Dark Souls II will be ‘viciously hard’ |publisher=venturebeat.com |date=2013-06-11 |accessdate=2013-08-02 |archive-date=2013-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130813002506/http://venturebeat.com/2013/06/11/e2-2013-dark-souls-2/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>最终《[[黑暗靈魂II|黑暗靈魂II]]》于2014年3月11日发布于[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]和[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]平台，PC版本也于2014年4月25日发布。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/dark-souls-2-gets-pc-release-date-dev-promises-increased-texture-resolution/1100-6418146/ |title=Dark Souls 2 gets PC release date, dev promises "increased texture resolution" |publisher=gamespot.com |accessdate=2014-09-01 |date=2014-04-06 |first=Eddie |last=Makuch |archive-date=2014-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141022121551/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/dark-souls-2-gets-pc-release-date-dev-promises-increased-texture-resolution/1100-6418146/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2015年又发布了增强版本“原罪哲人（Scholar of the First Sin），并在原先的平台的发布的同时，又新增[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]、[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]平台的版本。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Albert|first1=Brian|title=DARK SOULS II COMING TO XBOX ONE, PS4 NEXT YEAR|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/11/25/dark-souls-ii-coming-to-xbox-one-ps4-next-year|website=IGN|accessdate=2015-09-28|archive-date=2015-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151030033532/http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/11/25/dark-souls-ii-coming-to-xbox-one-ps4-next-year|dead-url=no}}</ref>魂系列的第三作《[[黑暗靈魂III|黑暗靈魂III]]》在2015年的[[E3电子娱乐展|E3]]展上公布，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theverge.com/2015/6/16/8788249/dark-souls-3-e3-2015-trailer-ps4-xbox-pc|title=Dark Souls 3 is bringing brutally hard battling back to PS4, Xbox One, and PC|publisher=''The Verge''|last=McCormick|first=Rich|date=2015-06-16|accessdate=2017-02-16|archive-date=2016-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161118032330/http://www.theverge.com/2015/6/16/8788249/dark-souls-3-e3-2015-trailer-ps4-xbox-pc|dead-url=no}}</ref>已于2016年4月12日发售。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Romano|first1=Sal|title=Dark Souls III launches April 2016 in North America and Europe|url=http://gematsu.com/2015/09/dark-souls-iii-launches-april-2016-north-america-europe#wbmQPEGiytctVdBV.99|publisher=Gematsu|accessdate=2015-09-17|archive-date=2015-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150918045413/http://gematsu.com/2015/09/dark-souls-iii-launches-april-2016-north-america-europe#wbmQPEGiytctVdBV.99|dead-url=no}}</ref>

